OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FVirtual legal assistants powered by
OL,7,Fartificial intelligence will be rolled
OL,8,Fout to Crown Courts across the country
OL,9,Fin an effort to tackle the backlog of
OL,10,Fcases.
OL,12,FThe AI assistants will be trialled in
OL,13,Fcontrolled environments before being
OL,14,Fused by judges and lawyers, the
OL,15,FMinistry of Justice (MoJ) said.
OL,17,FJudges will also have access to an AI
OL,18,Ftool for finding trial-ready cases and
OL,19,Fgrouping similar hearings together to
OL,20,Fmake the most of already stretched
OL,21,Fcourt time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
