OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister David Lammy will
OL,7,Fannounce the scheme at London Tech
OL,8,FWeek on Tuesday, where he will make
OL,9,Fthe case for how AI can drive criminal
OL,10,Fjustice system modernisation.
OL,12,FLammy said: "Artificial intelligence
OL,13,Fhas the power to transform how we
OL,14,Flive, work, and govern for the better.
OL,26,@tD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
