OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,F"This impact for good can be seen in
OL,7,Four justice system ` with thousands of
OL,8,Fdays of admin work saved for our
OL,9,Fprobation staff, and the advent of new
OL,10,Ftools which aim to cut court backlogs
OL,11,Fand deliver swifter justice for
OL,12,Fvictims."
OL,14,FThe former barrister is also set to
OL,15,Fannounce that probation officers in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales will be given access
OL,17,Fto an AI tool that automatically
OL,18,Frecords and transcribes conversations
OL,19,Fwith offenders.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
