OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised about the
OL,7,Fdangers of ramping up the use of AI,
OL,8,Fand especially what to do when it
OL,9,Fmakes a mistake.
OL,11,FA review into the banning of Maccabi
OL,12,FTel Aviv football fans from attending
OL,13,Fa football match against Aston Villa
OL,14,Fin November found an "AI
OL,15,Fhallucination" produced by Microsoft
OL,16,FCopilot had helped police justify the
OL,17,Fmove.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@NO]
