OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FThe error meant a non-existent game
OL,7,Fbetween Tel Aviv and West Ham had been
OL,8,Freferenced in a report produced by the
OL,9,Fpolice force prior to the game.
OL,11,FThe Law Society of England and Wales
OL,12,Fcalled on the government to make the
OL,13,Foutcome of any AI assistant trials
OL,14,Fpublic.
