OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FChief executive Ian Jeffery said: "We
OL,7,Fwelcome the MoJ's acknowledgement of
OL,8,Fthe importance of ensuring safe and
OL,9,Fethical use of any new tools,
OL,10,Fincluding AI.
OL,12,F"However, for the use of AI in the
OL,13,FCrown Court to be effective, the pilot
OL,14,Fmust be thoroughly evaluated. The
OL,15,Foutcomes of these evaluations, along
OL,16,Fwith the impact of AI on the justice
OL,17,Fsystem, should be made public.
OL,26,@nD@cOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
