CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,F"While new technology should enhance
OL,7,Faccess to justice, it cannot replace
OL,8,Fvital funding and additional court
OL,9,Fstaff.
OL,11,FThe number of cases waiting to be
OL,12,Fdealt with by crown courts in England
OL,13,Fand Wales hit a record high of more
OL,14,Fthan 80,000 cases earlier this year.
OL,16,FThis is more than double the level
OL,17,Fseen in 2019 (38,108), before the
OL,18,FCovid-19 pandemic.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
