OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FRecent figures show 2,600 crown court
OL,7,Ftrials in England and Wales were not
OL,8,Flisted until at least 2028, with 29
OL,9,Fnot due to be heard until 2030.
OL,11,FThe government has announced plans to
OL,12,Fscale back jury trials in a bid to
OL,13,Foverhaul the justice system and cut
OL,14,Fthe backlog.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,FAndrew Thomas KC, vice chair of the
OL,7,FCriminal Bar Association, welcomed the
OL,8,Fuse of AI tools in the criminal
OL,9,Fjustice system, and said many routine
OL,10,Ftasks "can be done quicker and more
OL,11,Fefficiently through the use of AI
OL,12,Ftools".
OL,14,FHe added: "There are obvious concerns:
OL,15,Fthe key is to educate judges, criminal
OL,16,Fbarristers and solicitors, and
OL,17,Finvestigators on the safe use of AI,
OL,18,Fso that its limitations are properly
OL,19,Funderstood by all.
OL,26,@rD@GOUtD@FO]vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,F"The quality of justice can never be
OL,7,Fwatered down by taking risks or
OL,8,Fshortcuts.
OL,10,F"In criminal law, AI is never going to
OL,11,Freplace the need for skilled criminal
OL,12,Fbarristers and solicitors as lawyers
OL,13,Fto review a case. Criminal law is all
OL,14,Fabout human interactions.
OL,16,F"AI tools lack the social and
OL,17,Femotional understanding reliably to
OL,18,Fidentify the significance of every
OL,19,Fpiece of evidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
