SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780966989
OL,3,C'AI legal assistants' to be trialled
OL,4,Cin courts to help tackle record backlog
OL,6,F"As all lawyers know, the devil is
OL,7,Falways in the detail, and AI tools
OL,8,Fshould not be used without checks and
OL,9,Fbalances."
